---
title: Grilled Shrimp Tacos with Foil Pouch Veggies and Lime Crema
description: Mexican food-lovers, unite! Seasoned shrimp and veggies cook perfectly on the grill, taking some of the heat out of the kitchen. Zesty lime crema adds a tangy finishing touch.

